The '''Vast Veldt''' was a region of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Cathar (location)/Legends|Cathar]]. It was a grassland devoid of any [[city-tree]]s or major natural formations, held much wildlife, and was the location for many [[Blood Hunt/Legends|blood hunts]].

